positive_prompt_structure: Photography style: photorealistic, professional photography, dslr quality
Subject: beautiful woman, detailed skin texture

negative_prompt_structure: Style rejection: cartoon, anime, illustration, 3d render

professional_prompting_tips.lighting_emphasis: Focus on 'natural lighting, studio lighting, cinematic lighting'
professional_prompting_tips.technical_quality: Include 'sharp focus, high resolution, 8k uhd, dslr quality'
professional_prompting_tips.skin_detail: Use 'detailed skin texture, realistic skin, natural skin'
professional_prompting_tips.composition: Add 'professional photography, magazine cover, editorial style'

workflow_flow.step_1: Load PornMaster Pony XL base model
workflow_flow.step_2: Apply CLIP skip (-2) for enhanced prompt following

expected_output.style: Professional erotic photography with natural lighting
expected_output.content: High-end explicit content with detailed skin and professional composition

artificial_lighting.solution: Emphasize 'natural lighting' in prompts, reduce 'cinematic' if too dramatic
artificial_lighting.alternative: Add 'studio lighting, professional lighting' for controlled results

skin_texture_issues.solution: Strengthen 'detailed skin texture, realistic skin' in positive prompt
skin_texture_issues.alternative: Increase steps to 35-40 for better detail rendering

composition_problems.solution: Add specific framing terms like 'close-up, full body, portrait'
composition_problems.alternative: Adjust aspect ratio or use different resolution

quality_inconsistency.solution: Ensure consistent prompt structure, check CLIP skip setting
quality_inconsistency.alternative: Use higher CFG (7.5-8.0) for more stable results

optimization_tips.lighting_consistency: Choose between natural or studio lighting and stick to it
optimization_tips.detail_enhancement: Combine technical quality terms with descriptive elements
optimization_tips.aspect_ratio: Portrait aspect works well for figure photography focus
